# CSS Styling Practice Project

A beginner CSS practice project built while learning web development fundamentals.

## 🔗 Live Demo
[View Project](https://earnest-dasik-e1c291.netlify.app/)

## 📌 About
This project was built as a hands-on exercise to practice core CSS styling concepts alongside HTML structure. It focuses on applying typography, color, and text styling to a basic webpage layout.

## 🛠️ Concepts Practiced
- CSS Fonts (font-family, font-size, font-weight)
- Text Styling (text-align, text-decoration, line-height, letter-spacing)
- Colors (color, background-color, hex and rgb values)
- Linking external CSS to HTML
- Basic page structure and layout

## 💻 Tech Stack
- HTML
- CSS

## 🚀 Deployment
Deployed using [Netlify](https://www.netlify.com/)

